.:: Einstein-puzzle ::.

There are 5 different favourite colors: blue, green, red, white, yellow
City: london, colone, san-francisco, new-york, miami
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: lacrosse-polo, parkour, baseball, basketball, lacrosse
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: bluemaster, dunhill, pall-mall, prince, blend
5 different pets are kept: cat, bird, dog, fish, horse
1. the person traveling to london is the person who likes red
2. the person traveling to swedish is the owner of the dog
3. the person traveling to colone is the person who's sport is basketball
4. the person who likes green is on the left of the person who likes white
5. the person who likes green is the person who's sport is parkour
6. the pall-mall-smoker is the owner of the bird
7. the person who likes yellow is the dunhill-smoker
8. the person who's sport is baseball is in the middle
9. the person traveling to new-york is on the far left
10. the blend-smoker is on the left or right of the owner of the cat
11. the owner of the horses is on the left or right of the dunhill-smoker
12. the bluemaster-smoker is the person who's sport is lacrosse-polo
13. the person traveling to san-francisco is the prince-smoker
14. the person traveling to new-york is on the left or right of the person who likes blue
15. the blend-smoker is on the left or right of the person who's sport is lacrosse

.:: Answer ::.
|		|	1	|	2	|	3	|	4	|	5	|
| Color		|    yellow	|     blue	|      red	|     green	|     white	|
| City	|   new-york	|    colone	|    london	|    san-francisco	|    swedish	|
| Pet		|     cat	|    horse	|     bird	|     fish	|      dog	|
| Sport	|    lacrosse	|     basketball	|     baseball	|    parkour	|      lacrosse-polo	|
| Cigar		|   dunhill	|    blend	|  pall-mall	|    prince	|   bluemaster	|
